1 SECTION 1. BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF MARYLAND,
2 That the Laws of Maryland read as follows:
3 Article – Education
4 5–244.
5 (A) THE GOVERNOR SHALL INCLUDE IN THE ANNUAL BUDGET BILL AN
6 APPROPRIATION IN THE FOLLOWING AMOUNTS TO THE DEPARTMENT FOR THE
7 COALITION FOR PUBLIC SAFETY TRAINING IN SCHOOLS, INC., TO BE USED FOR
8 INCREASING THE NUMBER OF STUDENTS WITH ACCESS TO DRIVER EDUCATION AND
9 CAREER AND TECHNICAL EDUCATION IN THE STATE:
