12 (3) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2029, $272,100;
13 (4) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2030, $276,400;
14 (5) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2031, $280,850; AND
15 (6) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2032, $216,600.
16 (B) (1) THE APPROPRIATIONS MADE IN ACCORDANCE WITH SUBSECTION
17 (A) OF THIS SECTION SHALL BE ALLOCATED AS SPECIFIED IN THIS SUBSECTION.
18 (2) THE FOLLOWING ALLOCATIONS SHALL BE USED TO SUPPORT
19 PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT FOR CAREER AND TECHNICAL EDUCATION
20 TEACHERS, ASSIST WITH TRANSPORTATION OF STUDENTS TO AND FROM CAREER
21 AND TECHNICAL EDUCATION TRAINING ACTIVITIES, AND SUPPORT CAREER AND
22 TECHNICAL EDUCATION IN SCHOOLS:
23 (I) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2027, $115,000;
24 (II) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2028, $115,300;
25 (III) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2029, $115,600;
26 (IV) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2030, $116,000;
27 (V) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2031, $116,250; AND

