1 (VI) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2032, $116,600.
2 (3) THE FOLLOWING ALLOCATIONS SHALL BE USED TO INCREASE THE
3 NUMBER OF STUDENTS WHO RECEIVE DRIVER EDUCATION TRAINING AND ASSIST IN
4 PROVIDING DRIVER EDUCATION TRAINING:
5 (I) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2027, $125,750;
