12 CAREER AND TECHNICAL EDUCATION EVENTS:
13 (I) FOR EACH OF FISCAL YEARS 2027 THROUGH 2031, $8,000;
14 AND
15 (II) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2032, $6,000.
